description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 21

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

The weakest groups from the food truck restaurant will face off against each other in a fierce kitchen showdown. Two teams will be safe, and the lowest three must cook again in a showdown leaving one team fighting for their spot in a sudden death cook-off.
